org.processmining.plugins.etconformance.data

Class PrefixAutomaton

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.processmining.plugins.etconformance.data.PrefixAutomaton

  • public class PrefixAutomaton
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a prefix automaton of a log. Eventually, this prefix could be enriched with model information.
    Author:
    Jorge Munoz-Gama (jmunoz)
